---
// JumboTextSection Component
---

<div class="body-block">
	<div class="content-container">
		<div class="jumbo-text-wrapper">
			<p class="jumbo-text">
				At Trailmerge, our vision is to promote abundance of life and opportunity. <br><br>
				This drives how we operate with our team members and our clients – mentorship and development are a core part of who we are. <br><br>
				This is also how we partner with our clients – journeying with internal teams to support their dreams for impact and their growth.<br>
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="decorative-line"></div>
	</div>
</div>

<style>
	.body-block {
		padding: 80px 0;
	}

	.content-container {
		padding: 0 20px;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.jumbo-text-wrapper {
		margin-bottom: 80px;
	}

	.jumbo-text {
		font-family: Bitter, serif;
		font-size: 28px;
		font-weight: 400;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--grey-5);
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 900px;
	}

	.decorative-line {
		background-color: var(--mint);
		width: 100%;
		height: 4px;
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.body-block {
			padding: 60px 0;
		}

		.jumbo-text {
			font-size: 28px;
		}

		.jumbo-text-wrapper {
			margin-bottom: 60px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.body-block {
			padding: 48px 0;
		}

		.content-container {
			padding: 0 16px;
		}

		.jumbo-text {
			font-size: 24px;
		}

		.jumbo-text-wrapper {
			margin-bottom: 48px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.body-block {
			padding: 40px 0;
		}

		.jumbo-text {
			font-size: 20px;
			line-height: 1.5;
		}

		.jumbo-text-wrapper {
			margin-bottom: 40px;
		}
	}
</style>
